# {PROJECT_NAME} .gitignore
# Initialized: 2026-05-28

# ============================================
# 1. SECURITY — HARD LINE
# No credentials, tokens, passwords, keys
# ============================================
.env
.env.*
*.env.md
.env.md
*.key
*.pem
id_rsa*
id_ed25519*
*_secret
*_token
*.ovpn
gcp-service-account.json
**/*service-account*.json
**/mcp.json
**/mcp.local.json
**/.credentials.json
**/.claude.json.backup.*
**/sudoers.d/
nopasswd*

# ============================================
# 2. THE VAULT — Folder + READMEs tracked, contents blocked
# ============================================
# Block all vault contents
5_THE_VAULT/*
!5_THE_VAULT/README*
!5_THE_VAULT/index.*

# project_family — completely restricted, no trace, no mention
5_THE_VAULT/project_family/

# ============================================
# 3. LARGE FILES — Size management
# GitHub hard limit: 100MB per file
# ============================================
# Disk images and ISOs (in THE_VAULT, double-blocked)
*.iso
*.img
*.qcow2
*.vmdk
*.ova
*.ovf
*.box
*.vbox
*.vdi
*.dmg

# KG/vector pipeline outputs — compiled data, often large
**/chunks/
**/embeddings/
**/raw_text/
**/entities_relations/

# Compiled knowledge graphs — regeneratable, often 50-245MB+
**/*knowledge_graph*.json

# Ollama model blobs — multi-GB ML weights, never commit
**/ollama/

# Gemini/agent runtime temp data (both legacy lowercase and current capitalized paths)
3_MEMORY_SYSTEMS/master_memory_bank/thread_mgmt/gemini/
3_MEMORY_SYSTEMS/master_memory_bank/thread_mgmt/ollama/
3_MEMORY_SYSTEMS/Master_Memory_Bank/thread_mgmt/gemini/
3_MEMORY_SYSTEMS/Master_Memory_Bank/thread_mgmt/ollama/

# Unity project build artifacts — entirely regeneratable, 1.2GB
2_AGENT_DEFINITIONS/Senior_Advisor/p.main_agent_audio_pipeline/Library/

# Large ML/data binary formats
*.pkl
*.bin
*.h5
*.hdf5
*.parquet
*.arrow
*.gguf
*.pt
*.safetensors
*.onnx
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

# Archive formats
*.tar.gz
*.zip
*.7z
*.bz2
*.xz

# ============================================
# 3b. OBSIDIAN — block plugins and device state entirely
# Plugin JS files are third-party binaries (20k-50k lines), not our code
# ============================================
.obsidian/plugins/
.obsidian/workspace.json
.obsidian/workspace-mobile.json
.obsidian/graph.json
.obsidian/cache
.trash/

# ============================================
# 3c. AUTOMATED AGENT OUTPUTS — not for public release repo
# News scans, daily reports, auto-generated logs belong in private repo
# ============================================
**/NEWS_ROOM/
**/*_scan_*.md
**/*morning_scan*
**/*midday_scan*
**/*evening_scan*
4_SHARED_RESOURCES/Reporting_Depot/thread_feedback_loop/report_*.md

# ============================================
# 4. AGENT RUNTIME DATA — Local only
# ============================================
# Claude Code CLI — block all runtime data, track only custom commands
# Root .claude/
.claude/conversations/
.claude/cache/
.claude/statsig/
.claude/telemetry/
.claude/paste-cache/
.claude/file-history/
.claude/sessions/
.claude/shell-snapshots/
.claude/todos/
.claude/ide/
.claude/projects/
.claude/history.jsonl
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
.claude/plugins/
# All nested .claude/ dirs (agent nodes) — block everything except commands/
**/.claude/conversations/
**/.claude/cache/
**/.claude/statsig/
**/.claude/telemetry/
**/.claude/paste-cache/
**/.claude/file-history/
**/.claude/sessions/
**/.claude/shell-snapshots/
**/.claude/todos/
**/.claude/ide/
**/.claude/projects/
**/.claude/history.jsonl
**/.claude/*.lock
**/.claude/.*
**/.claude/plugins/

# Agent runtime backups and embedded plugin repos
**/prime/backups/
**/watcher/backups/
**/plugins/superpowers/
**/plugins/marketplaces/
**/extensions/superpowers/

# Gemini CLI runtime
.gemini/

# ============================================
# 5. ARTIFACT / STAGING FILES
# ============================================
\#\#*
\#\#*/
**/\#\#*
**/\#\#*/

# ============================================
# 6. SYSTEM & IDE TRASH
# ============================================
.DS_Store
._*
Thumbs.db
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
venv/
.venv/
env/
node_modules/
